{"id":1949,"date":"2020-11-03T10:10:34","date_gmt":"2020-11-03T10:10:34","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/parliament.imarketing.com.na\/?page_id=1949"},"modified":"2021-06-03T12:14:02","modified_gmt":"2021-06-03T10:14:02","slug":"hansards","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/hansards\/","title":{"rendered":"Hansards"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1620174555865{background-color: #f4f4f4 !important;}&#8221;]<div id=\"ultimate-heading-60016848a4cf511dd\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-60016848a4cf511dd uvc-24  uvc-heading-default-font-sizes\" data-hspacer=\"no_spacer\"  data-halign=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left\"><div class=\"uvc-heading-spacer no_spacer\" style=\"top\"><\/div><div class=\"uvc-main-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-60016848a4cf511dd h2'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}' ><h2 style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Hansard Services<\/h2><\/div><\/div>[vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The two Houses, i.e. National Assembly and National Council, have specific people dealing with the Hansard. They are responsible for the recording, transcribing, editing, publication and distribution of the verbatim Official Reports of the Houses. The mission of Hansard Services is to provide a quality verbatim report of proceedings and provide editorial support to Members of Parliament.<\/div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">While the National Council has an in-house Hansard Division, the National Assembly outsourced its Hansard function.<\/div>\n<div><\/div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Hansard is the name of the official publication of the verbatim proceedings of a parliamentary body. It is a document that contains the exact same words spoken by Members of Parliament during a parliamentary session. The Parliament of Namibia publishes two separate sets of Hansards, i.e. for the National Assembly and for the National Council.<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text]<div id=\"ultimate-heading-93026848a4cf51221\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-93026848a4cf51221 uvc-2122  uvc-heading-default-font-sizes\" data-hspacer=\"no_spacer\"  data-halign=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left\"><div class=\"uvc-heading-spacer no_spacer\" style=\"top\"><\/div><div class=\"uvc-main-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-93026848a4cf51221 h2'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}' ><h2 style=\"font-weight:bold;\">National Assembly Hansard Services contact details<\/h2><\/div><div class=\"uvc-sub-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-93026848a4cf51221 .uvc-sub-heading '  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}'  style=\"font-weight:normal;\">Tel: +264 61 288 2510<\/p>\n<p>Fax: +264 61 2394910<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"mailto:library@parliament.na\">Email Us<\/a><\/div><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1620174555865{background-color: #f4f4f4 !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_text] The two Houses, i.e. National Assembly and National Council, have specific people dealing with the Hansard. They are responsible for the recording, transcribing, editing, publication and distribution of the verbatim Official Reports of the Houses. The mission of Hansard Services is to provide a quality verbatim report of proceedings and provide&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":8,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"class_list":["post-1949","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry","description-off"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1949","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https